revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yerbys}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yerby'' is the 24855<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1001 individuals. ''Yerby'' is most common among White (73.23%) and Black/African American (20.08%) individuals.
